			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Sounds like exp will be divided as follows:
<br />

<br />
60 units of XP/kill in 6 man group.  Add 80%=60+48=108.
<br />

<br />
108/5=21.xx XP units per group member.
<br />

<br />
60 units of XP/kill in 5 man group.  Add 60%  60+36=96.
<br />

<br />
96/5=19.xx XP units per group member.
<br />

<br />
So, even if you kill at the same rate, you get more exp over all in the full group.  Killing more rapidly only enhances the XP rate.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
