				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is how I see it:
<br />

<br />
Six-man group before this change:
<br />

<br />
120% / 6 = 20% XP for each member.
<br />

<br />
Six-man group after this change:
<br />

<br />
180% / 5 = 36% XP for each member.
<br />

<br />
This means it will only take 3 kills with group to surpass what you'd have gotten soloing mob (100%).  It would have taken 5 mobs just to equal solo XP before.  Very attractive I think.  This might be the end of soloing as we know it.
<br />

<br />
-Bawang</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
