				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">This might be the end of soloing as we know it. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
I was trying to figure out who benefits from this the most. Frankly I think it benefits mages alot.
<br />

<br />
We now still have the solo option, but are going to have a much smoother time getting in pick up groups, when desired.
<br />

<br />
Groups of 6 are going to become very hot. A damage dealer as person 6 is goign to be nothing but per xp gold for everyone, with no (mathmatical at least) drawback.
<br />

<br />
With some of my other chars, we frequently have tried to find that sweet spot, which is frequelty around 3 or 4 people in a group, but NOW, I mean you only have to kill 3x as fast with 6 people as one to out do soloing, thats going to be huge.
<br />

<br />
A 6 person group damn well better kill stuff 3 or so times faster than one person.<br />_________________<br /><b><a href = "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=651311&resize=true" target=_new>Vykon Incendium</a></b>
<br />
Magician, Zebuxoruk</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
