				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ok, let's look at this compared to the last time they increased the group XP bonus.
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
XP Formula used when EverQuest was first released&#58;
<br />

<br />
Members&nbsp; Bonus&nbsp; &nbsp; XP/kill&nbsp; &nbsp; Mobs/Time
<br />
1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;100%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1.00
<br />
2&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 51%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1.96
<br />
3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 35%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.88
<br />
4&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 27%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3.77
<br />
5&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 22%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4.63
<br />
6&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;22%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4.55</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
XP Formula used since 14/01/2001&#58;
<br />

<br />
Members&nbsp; Bonus&nbsp; &nbsp; XP/kill&nbsp; &nbsp; Mobs/Time
<br />
1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;100%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1.00
<br />
2&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 51%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1.96
<br />
3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 35%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.83
<br />
4&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;28%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3.64
<br />
5&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 14%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;23%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4.39
<br />
6&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 20%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;24%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4.17</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
XP Formula now implimented on Test&#58;
<br />

<br />
Members&nbsp; Bonus&nbsp; &nbsp; XP/kill&nbsp; &nbsp; Mobs/Time
<br />
1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;100%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1.00
<br />
2&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 20%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;60%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1.67
<br />
3&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 40%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;47%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.14
<br />
4&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 60%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;40%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.50
<br />
5&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 80%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;36%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.78
<br />
6&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 80%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;36%&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.78</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
Key:
<br />
<ul><li><span style="font-weight: bold">Members</span> - Number of Group Members
<br />
<li><span style="font-weight: bold">Bonus</span> - XP bonus granted above 100% for additional group member(s).
<br />
<li><span style="font-weight: bold">XP/kill</span> - Percentage of mobs XP granted to each group member on kill.
<br />
<li><span style="font-weight: bold">Mobs/Time</span> - Number of mobs that group would have to kill in the same time as any one group member could solo the mob in order to gain the same XP.</ul>
<br />
So what they're proposing is that a 5 or 6 person group will get more XP than a current 3 member group killing the same mobs at the same speed would now.
<br />

<br />
Any XP increase or increased demand to fill group slots regardless of class is good for everyone, and it looks like this time they're actually taking a more serious look at making players want to fill group slots.<br />_________________<br /><ul><li><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=279732" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Kantreach</a> - Arch Mage Antagonist - Tholuxe Paells<li><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59365" target="_blank" class="postlink">Kathodos</a> - Battle Cleric of Tunare - Tholuxe Paells</ul></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
